<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | You type the number into terminal, and the screen wakes up. What
<b>Floyd</b> | follows sends frigid whiplashes through your spine.
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">Initiative One (or First initiative)</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">All reunited, the Council of the Thirteen pledges eternal secrecy</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">upon this Initiative, which will not be traded, in any part, at any</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">cost.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">The icy mantle under Monarch (System KFS - Andromeda galaxy) has</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">been pierced. What the first human probes have found can only be</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">described as the remnants of a former civilization, the mortal spoils</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">of which can be trusted as ultimately lost. A series of globular</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">machines lays in a pattern (called the Hyeromatrix), hidden under the</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">very mantle of the earth. All forty-four of those machines (called the</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">Hyerotropes) are dormant but still present a form of "living"</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">electromagnetic and geo-gravitational power. Beyond this, an unknown</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">energy array seems to be pulsing inside them, out of the usual</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">spectrum. Whatever the structures are, there is indeed no way of</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">stating that they aren't alien in nature.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">Moreso, the radiance emitted by one of the bigger spheres is very</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">similar to the fast decaying fingerprints of the Event residue. This</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">MUST be noted as extremely important.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">As the coded memories recount, the Event Primeval was a</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">star-shattering event that devoured entirely our neighbor galaxy. An</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">energy pattern so similar could mean the Event can be replicated -- or</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">even controlled and slaved to one's benefit.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">The Andromeda colony came here from outer space many centuries</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">before the Event happened. We now have time to study and understand</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">how the Event started, to avoid this New Heaven being destroyed by</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">forces as of now uncontrollable. For this reason, a containment cage</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">will be closed around the forty-four Hyerotropes and investigative</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">labs will be built under the Monarch's crust.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">By order of the Council of the Thirteen, the cage will be named</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">"Construct" and the labs "the Settlements". For obvious secrecy</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">reasons, the real motives behind the two buildings will be concealed</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">from the population.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">Monarch Bastion Satellite, 12/05/8199.</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">(signed by the thirteen members of the Council)</span>
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | You stand, shocked.
<b>Floyd</b> |
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">So this is why they killed Andy. This is the secret they were</span>
<b>Floyd</b> | <span class="floydstyle em">trying to keep.</span>
